- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on identifying dialects in Arabic and German broadcast speech.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses deep learning models for the task.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with AI-based techniques for language processing.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with identifying language varieties and dialects, which can be useful in social and information networks.
